OL,3,CRifle recovered from Cardiff home as
OL,4,Celderly couple found dead named by
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FThe couple who died at a property in
OL,8,FCardiff have been named as Christine
OL,9,FJefferies, 72, and Stephen Jefferies,
OL,10,F74.
OL,12,FSouth Wales Police have recovered a
OL,13,Frifle from a property in the
OL,14,FTrowbridge area of the city where the
OL,15,Fhusband and wife were found dead on
OL,16,FSaturday.
OL,18,FDetectives say they are not currently
OL,19,Fseeking anyone else in connections
OL,20,Fwith their deaths. A dog was also
OL,21,Ffound deceased at the address.
