OL,7,FPolice are to supporting and updating
OL,8,Fthe family of Mr and Mrs Jefferies and
OL,9,Fsay enquiries are continuing to
OL,10,Festablish what happened.
OL,12,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,13,Fhouse in Morfa Crescent, at around
OL,14,F2.50pm on Saturday October 5.
OL,16,FDetective Chief Inspector Lianne Rees,
OL,17,Ffrom South Wales Police, said: "Our
OL,18,Fthoughts are with the family and
OL,19,Ffriends of Christine and Stephen
OL,20,FJefferies at this difficult time.
